              <h2>DESIGN AND PSYCHOLOGY</h2>
              <p style="text-align: none;">Design and psychology is all about people and their interaction with technology. This involves studying the influence products have on user behaviour or testing new designs for usability. We explore different areas of technology and try to make the experience better for people.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
              <div class="fact-item">
                  <img src="img/chemical.png" alt="Icon">
                  <h2>CHEMICAL ENGINEERING</h2>
                  <p>Chemical engineering shows paths to various interesting fields like Nanotechnology, Drug Delivery, Thermodynamics and Renewable energy among countless others. We aim to overcome some of the toughest challenges of the 21st century like climate change, vaccines, drinking water scarcity etc.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
