                  <h2>ELECTRONICS</h2>
                  <p>Electronics is a culmination of physics, nanomaterials, quantum mechanics, signal processing, circuit design and algorithms. We dive into the nano realm to make things like nanoscale devices, quantum computing, neuromorphic computing and so much more possible.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
              <div class="fact-item">
                  <img src="img/aero.png" alt="Icon">
                  <h2>AERODYNAMICS</h2>
                  <p>The rules of aerodynamics are a subset of fluid dynamics which explains how an aeroplane is able to fly, the reason behind designing rockets in a specific shape and much more. An uprising sector due to the recent interests in the commercialization of the space industry.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-6">
              <div class="fact-item">
                  <img src="img/bio.png" alt="Icon">
                  <h2>BIOTECHNOLOGY</h2>
                  <p>Biotechnology is the sweet spot between Biology, Technology and Engineering. It's the area of study responsible for production of medicines, environmental control, vaccines, cancer research and many more fields.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="fact-item">
              <img src="img/arm.png" alt="Icon">
              <h2>ROBOTICS</h2>
              <p>Robotics is an integration of maths, physics, and engineering fields. At RSM, we are focused on intense research in the fields of perception, planning, kinematics sprawling across autonomous systems, multi-agent systems, biomedical robots to name a few.</p>
          </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="offset-lg-3 col-lg-6">
              <div class="fact-item">
                  <img src="img/AI.png" alt="Icon">
                  <h2>ARTIFICIAL INTELLIGENCE</h2>
                  <p>AI is an interdisciplinary science with multiple approaches. Research in machine learning and deep learning has brought about a paradigm shift in virtually every aspect of life. At RSM, we dive into several sub-fields such as NLP, CV, Reinforcement Learning, GANs, Federated Learning and so much more.</p>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
